@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

[*] --> UserRequest

state "user request" as UserRequest
UserRequest : entry / receive request
UserRequest : do / identify user
UserRequest : exit / gather video suggestions

state "gather videos" as GatherVideos
GatherVideos : entry / user identified
GatherVideos : do / collect videos
GatherVideos : exit / add details

state "add details" as AddDetails
AddDetails : entry / videos gathered
AddDetails : do / add thumbnails and view counts
AddDetails : exit / prepare videos

state "send videos" as SendVideos
SendVideos : entry / details added
SendVideos : do / send videos to user
SendVideos : exit / [*]

UserRequest --> GatherVideos
GatherVideos --> AddDetails
AddDetails --> SendVideos

SendVideos --> [*]

@enduml
